id: pm-aems
title: "GH-455: pm health auto-selects an uninstalled Ollama embedding model then fails vector refresh"
description: "Dogfood GH-455: health auto-detected qwen3-embedding:0.6b without checking installation and the vector refresh failed 404 with a noisy warning. Duplicate check: searched embedding auto-detect — pm-wt0g/pm-xutw (closed) cover migration/reindex, not detection; no open overlap."
