comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-06T09:13:01.693Z",codex-agent,"Implementation start: live duplicate-safe search found pm-aems as canonical GH-455 item related to the current health/vectorization lane. Root cause confirmed in semantic-defaults: auto-discovery falls back to qwen3-embedding when ollama list has no installed embedding model, which can make health refresh attempt a model that is not installed."
  "2026-07-06T09:26:35.423Z",codex-agent,"Evidence: removed implicit fallback to qwen3-embedding when ollama list does not report an installed embedding model; health vectorization details now expose auto_ollama_defaults_skipped_reason=no_installed_embedding_model and remediation 'ollama pull qwen3-embedding:0.6b' or explicit config. Linked test passed; full coverage passed 264 files / 5436 tests / 100% statements branches functions lines; security scan and audit clean."
  "2026-07-06T09:52:59.534Z",codex-agent,"Review follow-up: applied Cubic/Gemini remediation wording improvement so health tells users to configure providers.ollama.model explicitly, with search.embedding_model framed as an optional override. Focused tests passed after the change: semantic-defaults, search-provider-store-selection, and health-command (93/93), plus pnpm typecheck."
